CallStackFrame.

	EXPORT ?  -------.  FRAME HEAD
	IMPORT           |
	...              |
	IMPORT           |
	RETURN ADDRESS   |
	LOCAL            |
	...              |
	LOCAL -----------'
	STACK -----------.  LOCAL STACK
	...              |
	STACK -----------'
